  gatheringCharacters:
  - characterName: Ozric
    characterObject: {fileID: 590094279}
    characterButton: {fileID: 590094281}
    characterRectTransform: {fileID: 590094280}
    normalPosition: {x: -690, y: -107}
    focusedPosition: {x: -690, y: -107}
    introLinesBeforeChoices:
    - The mantis notices you approaching.
    - His posture immediately straightens.
    - "\u201CThe newcomer.\u201D"
    - "\u201CIt is good to see another soul find their way here.\u201D"
    - "\u201CI am Ozric.\u201D"
    introSpeakerChanges:
    - lineIndex: 0
      speakerName: YOU
    - lineIndex: 1
      speakerName: YOU
    - lineIndex: 2
      speakerName: Ozric
    - lineIndex: 3
      speakerName: Ozric
    - lineIndex: 4
      speakerName: Ozric
    choices:
    - buttonText: How long have you been here?
      resultLines:
      - "\u201CLong enough.\u201D"
      - "\u201CTime doesn\u2019t matter. Purpose does.\u201D"
      - "\u201CSee you around. May the Flesh embrace you.\u201D"
      speakerChanges:
      - lineIndex: 0
        speakerName: Ozric
      - lineIndex: 1
        speakerName: Ozric
      - lineIndex: 2
        speakerName: Ozric
    - buttonText: "\u201CWho was that guy?\u201D"
      resultLines:
      - His eyes brighten
      - "\u201CA remarkable man.\u201D"
      - "\u201CWithout him, many of us would have perished.\u201D"
      - "\u201CI certainly would have.\u201D"
      - "\u201CSee you around. May the Flesh embrace you.\u201D"
      speakerChanges:
      - lineIndex: 0
        speakerName: YOU
      - lineIndex: 1
        speakerName: Ozric
      - lineIndex: 2
        speakerName: Ozric
      - lineIndex: 3
        speakerName: Ozric
      - lineIndex: 4
        speakerName: Ozric
    - buttonText: "\u201CWhat exactly is this place?\u201D"
      resultLines:
      - "\u201CHome.\u201D"
      - "\u201CFor those the world has abandoned.\u201D"
      - "\u201CSee you around. May the Flesh embrace you.\u201D"
      speakerChanges:
      - lineIndex: 0
        speakerName: Ozric
      - lineIndex: 1
        speakerName: Ozric
      - lineIndex: 2
        speakerName: Ozric
    hasTalkedToCharacter: 0
  - characterName: Bramble
    characterObject: {fileID: 942175340}
    characterButton: {fileID: 942175342}
    characterRectTransform: {fileID: 942175341}
    normalPosition: {x: 230, y: -249}
    focusedPosition: {x: -690, y: -107}
    introLinesBeforeChoices:
    - Before you can say a word, the beetle waves enthusiastically.
    - "\u201CYou made it!\u201D"
    - "\u201CWell obviously you made it.\u201D"
    - "\u201CYou\u2019re standing here!\u201D"
    - "\u201CI\u2019m Bramble \u2013 it is so pleasant to meet you!\u201D"
    introSpeakerChanges:
    - lineIndex: 0
      speakerName: YOU
    - lineIndex: 1
      speakerName: Bramble
    - lineIndex: 2
      speakerName: Bramble
    - lineIndex: 3
      speakerName: Bramble
    - lineIndex: 4
      speakerName: Bramble
    choices:
    - buttonText: You seem happy here
      resultLines:
      - "\u201CI am!\u201D"
      - "\u201CMost days anyway.\u201D"
      - "\u201CWell definitely talk again, comrade! It was a pleasure meeting you.\u201D"
      speakerChanges:
      - lineIndex: 0
        speakerName: Bramble
      - lineIndex: 1
        speakerName: Bramble
      - lineIndex: 2
        speakerName: Bramble
    - buttonText: How long have you been here?
      resultLines:
      - "\u201CThree years.\u201D"
      - "\u201COr four.\u201D"
      - "\u201CActually... maybe five.\u201D"
      - "\u201CWell definitely talk again, comrade! It was a pleasure meeting you.\u201D"
      speakerChanges:
      - lineIndex: 0
        speakerName: Bramble
      - lineIndex: 1
        speakerName: Bramble
      - lineIndex: 2
        speakerName: Bramble
      - lineIndex: 3
        speakerName: Bramble
    - buttonText: What do the people here do all day?
      resultLines:
      - "\u201CMostly work.\u201D"
      - "\u201CGather supplies, Pray, Eat, ...\u201D"
      - "\u201CAttend sacrif- well ceremonies...!\u201D"
      - "\u201C...\u201D"
      - "\u201CActually, maybe forget about the last part.\u201D"
      - "\u201CWell definitely talk again, comrade! It was a pleasure meeting you.\u201D"
      speakerChanges:
      - lineIndex: 0
        speakerName: Bramble
      - lineIndex: 1
        speakerName: Bramble
      - lineIndex: 2
        speakerName: Bramble
      - lineIndex: 3
        speakerName: Bramble
      - lineIndex: 4
        speakerName: Bramble
      - lineIndex: 5
        speakerName: Bramble
    - buttonText: What do the people here do all day?
      resultLines:
      - "\u201CMostly work.\u201D"
      - "\u201CGather supplies, Pray, Eat, ...\u201D"
      - "\u201CAttend sacrif- well ceremonies...!\u201D"
      - "\u201C...\u201D"
      - "\u201CActually, maybe forget about the last part.\u201D"
      - "\u201CWell definitely talk again, comrade! It was a pleasure meeting you.\u201D"
      speakerChanges:
      - lineIndex: 0
        speakerName: Bramble
      - lineIndex: 1
        speakerName: Bramble
      - lineIndex: 2
        speakerName: Bramble
    hasTalkedToCharacter: 0
  - characterName: Ash
    characterObject: {fileID: 967956426}
    characterButton: {fileID: 967956428}
    characterRectTransform: {fileID: 967956427}
    normalPosition: {x: 702, y: -15}
    focusedPosition: {x: -690, y: -107}
    introLinesBeforeChoices:
    - The ant sits alone.
    - "He doesn\u2019t acknowledge you at first."
    - Only when you sit down, he looks you up and down.
    - "\u201COh... Most people avoid me. I\u2019m Ash.\u201D"
    introSpeakerChanges:
    - lineIndex: 3
      speakerName: Ash
    choices:
    - buttonText: Why?
      resultLines:
      - "\u201CYou\u2019d have to ask them.\u201D"
      - "\u201CI suggest you don\u2019t hang around me, if you want the others to
        like you. Stay safe.\u201D"
      speakerChanges:
      - lineIndex: 0
        speakerName: Ash
      - lineIndex: 1
        speakerName: Ash
    - buttonText: Can I trust that guy?
      resultLines:
      - "\u201CYou mean the leader?\u201D"
      - "\u201C...\u201D"
      - "\u201CInteresting...\u201D"
      - "\u201C... that you\u2019re asking.\u201D"
      - "\u201CI suggest you don\u2019t hang around me, if you want the others to
        like you. Stay safe.\u201D"
      speakerChanges:
      - lineIndex: 0
        speakerName: Ash
      - lineIndex: 1
        speakerName: Ash
      - lineIndex: 2
        speakerName: Ash
      - lineIndex: 3
        speakerName: Ash
      - lineIndex: 4
        speakerName: Ash
    - buttonText: "\u201CWhy are you here?\u201D"
      resultLines:
      - "\u201CSame reason as everyone else.\u201D"
      - "\u201C...\u201D"
      - "\u201CI made a mistake.\u201D"
      - "\u201CI suggest you don\u2019t hang around me, if you want the others to
        like you. Stay safe.\u201D"
      speakerChanges:
      - lineIndex: 0
        speakerName: Ash
      - lineIndex: 1
        speakerName: Ash
      - lineIndex: 2
        speakerName: Ash
      - lineIndex: 3
        speakerName: Ash
