      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[2]'
      value: The loud sound echoes through the small hut before dying out quickly.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[3]'
      value: ...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[4]'
      value: "Silence. Not the kind you\u2019re used to."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[5]'
      value: Not the quiet of the night or the soft stillness of sleep.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[6]'
      value: This silence... it lingers. Heavy. Pressing.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[7]'
      value: ...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[8]'
      value: You stand still for a moment, hand still resting against the door hoping
        something might answer and break the tension.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[9]'
      value: Nothing does. Of course not.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[10]'
      value: You let your hand drop.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[11]'
      value: '*Jingle*'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[12]'
      value: The bells of your jester cap make an ironically cheerful sound as you
        pull it of and toss it onto the table.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[13]'
      value: Once, they sounded so bright and alive to you...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[14]'
      value: ...now they just sound dull. Like everything else.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[15]'
      value: "\u201CFitting.\u201D"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[16]'
      value: You step further into the room.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[17]'
      value: '*CREAAAK*'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[18]'
      value: The floorboards creak beneath your weight, louder than usual, as if
        they were laughing at you.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[19]'
      value: The air smells of damp wood and old straw.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[20]'
      value: A faint trace of mold clings to the corners of the walls.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[21]'
      value: ...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[22]'
      value: You sit down on the edge of your bed.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[23]'
      value: '*creak*'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[24]'
      value: It groans quietly in protest.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[25]'
      value: You stare down on the old wood floor, your arms supporting your body.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[26]'
      value: ...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[27]'
      value: Your thoughts are quiet.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[28]'
      value: You start to ponder on the meaning of your life.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[29]'
      value: What is the purpose now?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[30]'
      value: "You can still see the king\u2019s face in your mind... Bored. Distant."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[31]'
      value: A single motion with his hand and you were dismissed.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[32]'
      value: Just like that.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[33]'
      value: '*Huff*'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[34]'
      value: No coin. No position. No place to return to tomorrow.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[35]'
      value: No Purpose. Nothing Left
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[36]'
      value: Your eyes drift across the small room, searching without purpose, until
        they settle on the small wooden table lit by the bright moonlight.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[37]'
      value: '*Creak-creak*'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[38]'
      value: You walk over to the table to examine the bottle that caught your eye.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[39]'
      value: "\u201CRat Poison\u201D"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[40]'
      value: You stare at the yellowed label for a long moment.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[41]'
      value: "\u201CEven they get mercy in the end.\u201D"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[42]'
      value: You turn the cold bottle slightly, watching the dark liquid shift inside.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[43]'
      value: After a moment of hesitation, you pull out the cork separating you and
        the substance which will free you from this pain.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[44]'
      value: Slowly... you bring the opening of the bottle closer to your mouth.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8269895852001782025, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'introDialogueLines.Array.data[45]'
      value: "\u201CThis is it. This is how it \u2013 \u201C*KNOCK*"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8392777103826453233, guid: 731684afd6d8913489f07d461455a505, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_IsActive
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
